			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use the debugbook options for the Murder Tribunal (act 3/LOW) to start the trial and go to the abattoir (Valeria can either be already dead or alive, it doesn't matter)\r\n- Alternatively, use ReCon command \"oe MT_Baptism\" and \"oe MT_Court\"\r\n- Kill Valeria if she's alive, otherwise step into the font of blood if she's already dead\r\n- You will become an Unholy Assassin - a few seconds after the wrap-up dialogue, this PAD will play."
				},
				"defaultAttitudes": [
					{}
				],
				"defaultEmotions": [
					{}
				],
